<p><iframe src="https://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--code/info%3Astyle/5" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>Title:</strong> Nobody in Their Right Mind<br />
<strong>Author:</strong> <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609721415" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;">Tufto</a></span>. This tale is part of the <a href="/the-man-who-wasnt-there-hub">Man Who Wasn't There</a> canon, and is the final entry of the main series. More of Tufto's work can be found <a href="/tufto-personnel-file">here</a>.<br />
